article_id:1317,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Maintenance Notice for 5/24(PT) [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590386400"></span>]</strong></span><br>The maintenance is now complete.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send the following items to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590375600"></span>.<br><br>・Exquisite Honey x3<br>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x3<br><br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><hr><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1589868000"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>The maintenance times in this notification will be changed as follows.<br><br>Before:<br>Approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590379200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590386400"></span><br><br>After:<br>Approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590375600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590386400"></span><br><br>Thank you for your patience.</div><hr><div>We will be performing server maintenance during the following period. You will not be able to obtain rewards if you complete a quest during the maintenance period. Please also claim any 30-Day Pack (Recovery) rewards before maintenance begins.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maintenance Period</div><div>Around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590379200"></span> to around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1590386400"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You will not be able to play Dragalia Lost during the maintenance.</div><div>2. Maintenance may start and/or end before or after the scheduled times.</div><div><br></div><div><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1589781600,update_time1590386409